<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.2.1">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2022-06-19T22:13:37-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/feed.xml</id><title type="html">Hermosawave Photography</title><subtitle>A series of daily landscape photographs by Daniel Sofer, over 18 years running.</subtitle><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><entry><title type="html">Sunset at 22nd St.</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220619/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Sunset at 22nd St." /><published>2022-06-19T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2022-06-19T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/twentysecond</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220619/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
  A clear evening, rare in June. It&apos;s a few days before the summer equinox, so the sun is far to the north, and sets over the Malibu coast.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
 &lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
6月には珍しい晴天の夕方。夏至の数日前なので、太陽は北のマリブ海岸の上に沈んでいる。
  &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Beach" /><summary type="html">A clear evening, rare in June. It&apos;s a few days before the summer equinox, so the sun is far to the north, and sets over the Malibu coast.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R09415-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R09415-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Green Belt</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220616/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Green Belt" /><published>2022-06-16T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2022-06-16T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/greenbelt</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220616/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
  Looking south from Pier Avenue, down the Hermosa Beach green belt, a former railroad line from a century ago.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
 &lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 ピアアベニューから南を見ると、エルモサビーチのグリーンベルト、100年前の旧鉄道路ことがある。
  &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Foliage" /><summary type="html">Looking south from Pier Avenue, down the Hermosa Beach green belt, a former railroad line from a century ago.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R09282.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R09282.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Portuguese Bend</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220611/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Portuguese Bend" /><published>2022-06-11T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2022-06-11T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/bend</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220611/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
  Looking out over Portuguese Bend and the Rancho Palos Verdes coastline.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
 &lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 Portuguese BendとRancho Palos Verdesの海岸線を望む。

  &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Palos Verdes" /><category term="Views" /><summary type="html">Looking out over Portuguese Bend and the Rancho Palos Verdes coastline.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R08968.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R08968.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Palos Verdes</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220610/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Palos Verdes" /><published>2022-06-10T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2022-06-10T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/pvgolf</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220610/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
  After weeks of Kyoto&apos;s lush greenery, it&apos;s a shock to return to Southern California, desert-by-the-sea. Coastal fog gives this scene a little mystery.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
 &lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 京都の豊かな緑に囲まれた数週間後、南カリフォルニアの海沿いの砂漠に戻ると衝撃を受ける。海岸の霧がこのシーンにちょっとした神秘性を与えている。
  &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Palos Verdes" /><category term="Views" /><summary type="html">After weeks of Kyoto&apos;s lush greenery, it&apos;s a shock to return to Southern California, desert-by-the-sea. Coastal fog gives this scene a little mystery.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R08960-Pano.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R08960-Pano.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Zenkokuji・善國寺</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220608/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Zenkokuji・善國寺" /><published>2022-06-08T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2022-06-08T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kagurazaka</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220608/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
  Gate in front of Zenkokuji Temple in Tokyo&apos;s Kagurazaka district.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
  東京・神楽坂にある善国寺の門前。
  &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Tokyo" /><category term="Temples" /><summary type="html">Gate in front of Zenkokuji Temple in Tokyo&apos;s Kagurazaka district.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R08945.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R08945.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Garden Waterfall・庭園の滝</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220607/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Garden Waterfall・庭園の滝" /><published>2022-06-07T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2022-06-07T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/new-otani</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220607/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
  The Japanese garden at the New Otani Hotel Tokyo. The garden dates back to the Edo era when it was part of a samurai lord’s mansion.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
ニューオータニホテル東京にある庭園。江戸時代、武家屋敷の一部として造られたものです。
  &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Tokyo" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Gardens" /><summary type="html">The Japanese garden at the New Otani Hotel Tokyo. The garden dates back to the Edo era when it was part of a samurai lord’s mansion.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R08896-Pano.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R08896-Pano.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Golden Station・金色駅</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220604/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Golden Station・金色駅" /><published>2022-06-04T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2022-06-04T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/tokyo-station</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220604/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
  Golden Hour sun lights up the classic façade of Tokyo Station.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
 東京駅前のマジックアワー。
  &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Tokyo" /><category term="Golden Hour" /><category term="Architecture" /><category term="Trains" /><summary type="html">Golden Hour sun lights up the classic façade of Tokyo Station.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R08822.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R08822.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Shohama Beach・小浜海岸</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220603/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Shohama Beach・小浜海岸" /><published>2022-06-03T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2022-06-03T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/hayama</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220603/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
  Last light looking out over Sagami Bay on the Shonan coast. Enoshima Island can be seen in the distance.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
 湘南海岸の相模湾を見下ろす夕暮れ時。遠くに江ノ島が見える。
  &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Tokyo" /><category term="Dusk" /><summary type="html">Last light looking out over Sagami Bay on the Shonan coast. Enoshima Island can be seen in the distance.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R08690.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R08690.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Iris Field・菖蒲田</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220602/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Iris Field・菖蒲田" /><published>2022-06-02T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2022-06-02T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/iris-field</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220602/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
 Irises in bloom at the Meiji Jingu Iris Field.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
 　明治神宮菖蒲田に咲き誇る花菖蒲。
  &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Tokyo" /><category term="Flowers" /><summary type="html">Irises in bloom at the Meiji Jingu Iris Field.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R08566.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R08566.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Shibuya Sunset・渋谷の夕焼け</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220601/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Shibuya Sunset・渋谷の夕焼け" /><published>2022-06-01T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2022-06-01T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/shibuya</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220601/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
 Setting sun and lots of video billboards above Shibuya Crossing this evening.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
 今夜の夕焼けと、渋谷交差点の上にあるたくさんの映像看板。
  &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Tokyo" /><category term="Sunset" /><summary type="html">Setting sun and lots of video billboards above Shibuya Crossing this evening.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R08527-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R08527-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>